  <h2 class="heading-two">Global over-rides</h2>

  <p>If you want all tooltips to be toggle or follow-mouse variations, you can open up <code>tooltip.js</code> and change the settings at the top:</p>

  <pre>var followMouse       = false;
var toggleTooltips    = false;</pre>

  <p>Changing these settings will over-ride all tooltips to follow the mouse or to be toggleable without having to add in the required <code>data</code> attributes.</p>

